body.description: CERRXIAN multifunctional desktop switch controller can be connected to computer host, speakers, mouse, keyboard, mobile hard disk, card reader, earphone, U disk, etc. to provide more extended practicality, support data transmission, one-key start/restart, with audio interface USB3.0 high-speed transmission, USB3.0 interface, the theoretical speed can reach 5Gbps, large files can be transmitted in seconds, and multiple USB interface devices can be connected at the same time Great replacement for broken switches on consoles, making it easier to start your computer if it's placed in a hard-to-reach area With the desktop mobile switch, the chassis can be completely locked, and you can press the power on, restart and other buttons on the desktop mobile switch, so that thieves who disassemble the machine and steal valuable parts such as CPU, memory, and graphics card have no way to start. Note: Before purchasing, please check the model of the computer motherboard and determine the position of each port. Without these ports, it cannot be used normally. Specifications: USB2.0 interface USB3.0 interface Type-C interface 3.5 TRRS interface On/off button Reset button Color: Black Outer cable length: 110cm/3.6ft Inner cable length: 30cm/11.8in
